de.interactive_instruments.model.std

Interface Id

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultId

    public interface Id
extends java.lang.Comparable
    An universal interface for identifying domain model items. The interface enables the usage of unique (UUID) and non-unique identifiers (String). The implementor decides on which type is generated, the clients of this interface obtain a uniform access.
